mp;u=https://www.walmart.com/ip/1129434332\u0026amp;subId1=subid_value\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e                        \u003c/p\u003e              \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eLego\u0026#39;s Technic sets are usually based on real cars and motorcycles, but occasionally the designs recreate popular vehicles from movies such as the \u003ca href=\"https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.walmart.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F565706%2F9383%3Fveh%3Daff%26sourceid%3Dimp_000011112222333344%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2F1129434332%26subId1%3Dsubid_value\u0026amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-batman-batcycle-lego-set-is-40-off-at-walmart-sold-out-everywhere-else%2F1100-6528148%2F\u0026amp;event_type=click\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eBatcycle from the 2022 film The Batman\u003c/a\u003e. This is a more complex build than the average Lego set with similar piece counts, but it serves as a good introduction to the Technic line and is recommended for kids ages nine and up.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThroughout the build, you\u0026#39;ll create \u0026#34;functional\u0026#34; steering and suspension systems as well as an articulating H4 engine, which connects to the back wheel with help of the chain drive.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis is a pretty decent-sized display model; the completed build is 13 inches long, 6.5 inches tall, and 4.5 inches wide.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere\u0026#39;s also a Lego Technic build of the Batmobile from The Batman. The 1,360-piece Batmobile originally retailed for $100, but it\u0026#39;s no longer in production, which means you typically need to spend a bit more to get the Batmobile from a reseller. At the moment, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Technic-Batman-Batmobile-Building/dp/B09FM4N3Y1?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Technic Batmobile is available for $135\u003c/a\u003e on Amazon.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e                      \u003c/div\u003e                                                                     \u003cdiv\u003e             \u003ch2\u003e                    \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure/dp/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{\u0026#34;destUrl\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure\\/dp\\/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;dwLinkTag\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;leadType\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;deal\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;linkLocation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;BuyButton\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;seamlessScrollPage\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;searchDim\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;}\" data-track-page-event=\"{\u0026#34;eventName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Monetization Link Clicked\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure/dp/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\"\u003eLego Batman Construction Figure \u0026amp; Bat-Pod Bike (713 Pieces)\u003c/a\u003e       \u003c/h2\u003e                                   \u003ch3\u003e                      \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure/dp/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{\u0026#34;destUrl\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure\\/dp\\/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;dwLinkTag\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;leadType\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;deal\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;linkLocation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;BuyButton\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;seamlessScrollPage\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;searchDim\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;}\" data-track-page-event=\"{\u0026#34;eventName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Monetization Link Clicked\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure/dp/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\"\u003e$52 (was $65)\u003c/a\u003e         \u003c/h3\u003e                                                                                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_medium/1595/15950357/4407664-legobatpod.png\"/\u003e                             \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure/dp/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{\u0026#34;destUrl\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure\\/dp\\/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;dwLinkTag\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;leadType\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;deal\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;linkLocation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;BuyButton\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;seamlessScrollPage\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;searchDim\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;}\" data-track-page-event=\"{\u0026#34;eventName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Monetization Link Clicked\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Batman-Construction-Motorcycle-Adventure/dp/B0CRWFG98V?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e                        \u003c/p\u003e              \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you prefer the Bat-Pod from The Dark Knight, Amazon has the Batman Construction Figure and Bat-Pod Bike set for 20% off, dropping the price from $65 down to $52. This is the best price yet for this cool 713-piece kit that released in August.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis is part of the Lego DC Batman line, so the Bat-Pod build isn\u0026#39;t nearly as in-depth mechanically. That said, you will build stud shooters for Batman to deploy when he\u0026#39;s attached to the bike.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe 10-inch Batman figure is one of the newest additions to Lego\u0026#39;s fun series of buildable superhero action figures. Construction Figures are multi-jointed, so you can move Batman\u0026#39;s arms, legs, and hips to create different poses. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis isn\u0026#39;t the first Batman Construction Figure. Last year, Lego released a figure based on the Caped Crusader\u0026#39;s appearance in Batman Returns. The \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Construction-Buildable-Jointed-Authentic/dp/B0BSRFTW75?tag=gamespot-bfcm-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eBatman Returns Construction Figure is on sale for $26.39\u003c/a\u003e (was $33) at Amazon.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e                      \u003c/div\u003e   \u003c/div\u003e\n  \n                        \n    \n        \n        \n  \n                                  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n          \n        \n        \n  \n                    \n  \n    \n          \n            \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003eGot a news tip or want to contact us directly? Email \u003ca href=\"mailto:news@gamespot.com?subject=Hi GameSpot! I have a news tip for you!\"\u003enews@gamespot.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \n      \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n      \u003c/section\u003e\n    \n            \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n  \n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n                      \u003cmeta itemprop=\"seamless-content-list-items\" data-list-item